<BLOCK1><TI>ORDER</TI>
<P>THIS APPEAL, commenced by the Defendants (Appellants), 2487048 Ontario Limited, Mike Allen and Clark Kent from the Judgment of Justice R. Cary Boswell of the Superior Court of Justice dated November 27, 2017, and from the Judgment of Justice R. Cary Boswell of the Superior Court of Justice dated March 7, 2018 was heard on Wednesday October 3, 2018 at the Osgoode Hall, 130 Queen Street West, Toronto, Ontario, M5H 2N5, with the judgement being reserved to this day.</P>
<P>ON READING the Appeal Book and Compendium for the Appellant, Compendium of the Plaintiff (Respondents) and Book of Authorities for the Appellant, the Exhibit Book for the Appellant and the Factums of both the Appellants and Respondents and on hearing the submissions of the lawyer(s) for the parties,</P>
<P>1. <BOLD>THIS COURT ORDERS</BOLD> that the within appeal is dismissed.</P>
<P>2. <BOLD>THIS COURT ORDERS</BOLD> that the Appellants pay the Respondents their costs of the appeal fixed in the amount of $12,500.00 inclusive of disbursements and HST.</P>
<P>3. <BOLD>THIS ORDER</BOLD> bears interest of the rate of 3 percent per year commencing on the date of this Order.</P>
