<P>ON READING the Notice of Motion, and the Affidavit herein, and on reviewing the Consent filed,
<P1>1. THIS COURT ORDERS that the Defendants/Appellants 2847048 ONTARIO LIMITED, MIKE ALLEN and CLARK KENT are hereby granted leave to serve and file an Amended Notice of Appeal by Friday, May 18<SUP>th</SUP>, 2018.</P1>
